			<div class="contents">
				<p>MEN's TEAM</p>

<p>Rules:</p>
<ol>
<li>Format Of Play : singles(A vs X),singles(B vs Y), doubles and reverse singles(A vs Y & B vs X).</li>
<li>All games will be best of 5.</li>
<li>Players playing singles won't be allowed to repeat in doubles.</li>
<li>Maximum number of 5 and minimum number of 4 players are allowed in a team.</li>
</ol>
<br><br>
<p>WOMEN TEAM</p>

<p>Rules</p>
<ol>
<li>It is a team event requiring a minimum of 3 players and a maximum of 4 players.</li>
<li>The event will consist of 5 sets and every set will comprise 5 games of 11 points each.</li>
<li>Description of the 5 sets is as follows:
<br>First two sets are singles matches,to be played by two different players A and B.
<br>Third set is a doubles match, to be played by either two new players (C and D) or one new player(C or D) and and one of the single players(A or B).
<br>The fourth and fifth set are reverse singles matches to be played by players(A and B).
</li>
</ol>
